&quot;Thanatos is bloated with power that is not his. He thinks he is death or goodness sake. One isnot death, one cannot be death, one can only be a vessel, and one can bring it. If I do not snip the thread with my shear,a person cannot die, even if Thanatos were to go to them and wrap his hands around there face. Surly you, the Allmighty God of the Underworld understand that.&quot;<br>
